{
  "2184670": {
    "name": "AbsentedAge2:アブセンテッドエイジ２ ～亡霊少女のローグライクアクションSRPG -依代の章- Demo",
    "steam_appid": 2184670,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184670/extras/705c7fa6aed2e114807a0c5e9a1a26b4.webp?t=1756058904\" width=380 height=38 /></span>　</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >――　你化为了无名少女，无名少女化为了你。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184670/extras/705c7fa6aed2e114807a0c5e9a1a26b4.webp?t=1756058904\" width=380 height=38 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>【这是什么样的游戏？】</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >AbsentedAge是新式复合型游戏，在非战斗时是ARPG，而在战斗中则会转换为SRPG（Rougelike模式）。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >只要接触敌人或者进行／受到先制攻击，就会无缝切换到回合制战斗模式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184670/extras/eda2ca7341f0025f26d81e32d5afd203.avif?t=1756058904\" width=487 height=124 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184670/extras/9e9bef79d7e954eee07efd5a1ce92915.webp?t=1756058904\" width=53 height=240 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184670/extras/53e2b05d7d49c47a255d41d2b6956979.poster.avif?t=1756058904\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184670/extras/53e2b05d7d49c47a255d41d2b6956979.webm?t=1756058904\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184670/extras/53e2b05d7d49c47a255d41d2b6956979.mp4?t=1756058904\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184670/extras/5d7dfc2394963c94c404aaf1cb21585f.webp?t=1756058904\" width=53 height=240 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过使用多达数百种富有战略性的技能与物品，一边更换各种华丽服饰，一边打倒各类棘手的怪物吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 由主人公们的“茶道乐队社”所演绎的互动BGM表现，将进一步点燃故事的热情。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >★本作为前作《幽玄之章》的续篇，支持继承通关存档。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >同时，好评如潮的教程系统在本作中也已配备，即便是初次游玩也能安心上手。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184670/extras/705c7fa6aed2e114807a0c5e9a1a26b4.webp?t=1756058904\" width=380 height=38 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在本作中，可使用能够召唤出在故事中产生了羁绊的好友共同作战的“助战召唤”，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以及可进行临时交替出战以脱离险境的“交接召唤”，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >它们的运用时机将左右你的战略走向。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184670/extras/9e9bef79d7e954eee07efd5a1ce92915.webp?t=1756058904\" width=53 height=240 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184670/extras/c2d90e6fe9ccfc7f29daca79209a417f.poster.avif?t=1756058904\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184670/extras/c2d90e6fe9ccfc7f29daca79209a417f.webm?t=1756058904\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184670/extras/c2d90e6fe9ccfc7f29daca79209a417f.mp4?t=1756058904\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184670/extras/5d7dfc2394963c94c404aaf1cb21585f.webp?t=1756058904\" width=53 height=240 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >请熟练运用半蓄力攻击、反击、精准格挡、攻击定身位移等脱离流派束缚的进阶技巧，展现你独具一格、打动人心的玩法吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >只要遵守另行公布的使用准则，就可以自由公开本作的游戏实况。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>【故事梗概】</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >失去了记忆与实体的幽灵少女(你)于记忆的异世界“禁领”中苏醒。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过与在禁领中相遇的精灵塔鲁特一同收集记忆—— </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你了解到自己原本是一名叫做“香恋”的小号手，正梦想着在今年夏天的超大型音乐盛会“超乐祭”中出演，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >此外你还了解到，即便是世间流传着你的死亡传闻的现在，你的乐队伙伴们也依旧在不懈的寻找你。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184670/extras/78e91540d6b34d30eded99248024eb6f.avif?t=1756058904\" width=400 height=400 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在与于街道和禁领中蚕食人心的神秘怪物耿鬼们激战之后，你夺回了失去的心之碎片中的一半。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随后在神秘组织“艾利西欧教会”的精灵使弥生的帮助下，你习得了足以在现世中实体化的能力——虽尚不完美。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >接下来，舞台来到了沉睡着“香恋”众多记忆的校园。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >而在那里，掌控着你的过往的更为巨大的异变，正潜藏在记忆之海的深处，静候你的到来—— </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184670/extras/705c7fa6aed2e114807a0c5e9a1a26b4.webp?t=1756058904\" width=380 height=38 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>【瞩目点】</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>◆与伙伴们一同携手</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >包括能够使用强力反击技能，擅长将困境化为机会的“隼人”与 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以放置可自主行动的炮台为核心，擅长阵地战的“铃”等等等等...... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与伙伴们在故事中产生的羁绊将通过精灵石在禁领中显现，并为你的冒险提供强大助力。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过装备不同的精灵石可改变ARPG模式下的地图动作，并拓宽你的战术选择。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184670/extras/9e9bef79d7e954eee07efd5a1ce92915.webp?t=1756058904\" width=53 height=240 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184670/extras/9b387ae1f1586f0d1e44ea5a892ae41e.poster.avif?t=1756058904\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184670/extras/9b387ae1f1586f0d1e44ea5a892ae41e.webm?t=1756058904\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184670/extras/9b387ae1f1586f0d1e44ea5a892ae41e.mp4?t=1756058904\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184670/extras/5d7dfc2394963c94c404aaf1cb21585f.webp?t=1756058904\" width=53 height=240 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >能够切换你的搭档——精灵塔鲁特的战斗风格的精灵术依旧健在。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过新增的技能树，还能进一步延伸追击或自动恢复等长处</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184670/extras/c482b27958b4dceafa7430ddad3acd9a.avif?t=1756058904\" width=640 height=360 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>◆丰富的装备与换装要素</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >所有新加入的立绘均为全新绘制。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作中同样拥有大量异常状态差分与装备换装部件。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次拾取同一件装备时，其熟练度(+值)都会上升，即便装备丢失熟练度也会保留，尽情尝试新的组合，享受外观定制的乐趣吧。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184670/extras/9e9bef79d7e954eee07efd5a1ce92915.webp?t=1756058904\" width=53 height=240 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184670/extras/f8432449069858eaa88b4276bf4ae578.poster.avif?t=1756058904\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184670/extras/f8432449069858eaa88b4276bf4ae578.webm?t=1756058904\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184670/extras/f8432449069858eaa88b4276bf4ae578.mp4?t=1756058904\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184670/extras/5d7dfc2394963c94c404aaf1cb21585f.webp?t=1756058904\" width=53 height=240 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184670/extras/705c7fa6aed2e114807a0c5e9a1a26b4.webp?t=1756058904\" width=380 height=38 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>【前作看这里】</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >→『AbsentedAge: 亡灵少女的方格世界 -幽玄之章-』（AbsentedAge: Squarebound）</p>",
